### Distribuicao de moedas
POST http://localhost:8080/api/transacoes/distribuicao
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN_PROFESSOR}}

{
  "professorId": "aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa",
  "alunoId": "bbbbbbbb-bbbb-bbbb-bbbb-bbbbbbbbbbbb",
  "valor": 50,
  "mensagem": "Reconhecimento por participacao"
}

### Extrato resumo aluno
GET http://localhost:8080/api/extratos/alunos/bbbbbbbb-bbbb-bbbb-bbbb-bbbbbbbbbbbb/resumo
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN_ALUNO}}

### Resgate de vantagem
POST http://localhost:8080/api/resgates
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN_ALUNO}}

{
  "alunoId": "bbbbbbbb-bbbb-bbbb-bbbb-bbbbbbbbbbbb",
  "vantagemId": "dddddddd-dddd-dddd-dddd-dddddddddddd"
}
